hello,i solved the problem,you should:
pip3 uninstall thop or conda uninstall thop,because total_ops param was registed to the model, when you use htop get param or mac.in fact ,in the project ,in file utils/torch_utils.py try to use htop.

Uninstalling thop worked for me too.
I tried both

`pip uninstall thop`

and

`conda uninstall thop`
